@AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5241

### Health Check
GET {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Health
Accept: application/json

### Database Status
GET {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Health/database
Accept: application/json

### Debug Info (shows all users)
GET {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Health/debug
Accept: application/json

### Register Test User
POST {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test@12345",
  "farmName": "Test Farm"
}

### Login Test
POST {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test@12345",
  "skipOTP": false
}

### Admin Login Test
POST {{AgriTrackAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin@12345",
  "skipOTP": true
}

###

